s with AEC firms to help them develop dynamic leaders. General George C. Marshall was one of the most influential and productive leaders of our time. His leadership strategies helped him to reorganize the entire US Army to make it run more efficiently. EMI has studied Marshall\u2019s framework and has distilled it into a number of steps that can be implemented within AEC firms to develop their leaders.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This complimentary webinar will give you a framework for developing AEC leaders better (and faster) than other firms. Failure to join us may set your firm\u2019s growth back years.<\/span><\/p>","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"section"},{"id":"11cd4411","settings":{"editor":"<p class=\"fl-heading\"><b>Your Presenter<\/b><\/p>","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"700","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"30","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","__globals__":{"text_color":"globals\/colors?id=primary"}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"7ad4ac93","settings":{"editor":"<h2 class=\"fl-heading\"><b>Anthony Fasano, P.E., AEC PM | Engineering Management Institute<\/b><\/h2>","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"66655488","settings":{"editor":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Anthony-Fasano.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-55130 size-medium\" title=\"Anthony Fasano, P.E., AEC PM\" src=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Anthony-Fasano-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"EMI- Your Engineering Career\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" \/><\/a><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Most AEC organizations are too busy to focus on attracting, developing, and retaining talented professionals, making it hard to grow. Through his work a tEMI, Fasano utilizes a proven framework to help organizations, both public and private, build professional development plans, programs, and tools that help them attract, build, AND maintain strong teams and grow sustainably.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fasano has written a bestselling book entitled <\/span><b><i>Engineer Your Own Success <\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(by IEEE-Wiley Press)<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, and under his stewardship, EMI has built a massive content platform including 10 active podcasts, 3 YouTube channels, and a popular blog dedicated to helping AEC professionals become better managers and leaders.<\/span><\/p>","_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"50","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"}],"settings":{"template":"elementor_canvas"},"metadata":{"_yoast_wpseo_content_score":"90","be_title_toggle_hide":"1","_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes":"2","disable_sitewide_popup":"a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"true\";}","_yoast_wpseo_wordproof_t